                    use, share, store and protect your personal information and how you can manage your personal
                    information.</p>
                <p>Before you start using our services, please be sure to read and understand this policy carefully. In
                    particular, you should read our bold/bold underlined terms to ensure that you fully understand and
                    agree to it before you start using it. For the professional vocabulary involved in this policy, we
                    try our best to explain it to you in a concise and popular way to facilitate your understanding. If
                    you have any questions, comments or suggestions about the content of this policy, you can contact us
                    through our website: http://www.istreamlab.com/.</p>
                <p>This privacy policy will help you understand the following:</p>
                <ol>
