                    <li>How we collect and use your information</li>
                    <li>How do we share, transfer, and publicly disclose your information</li>
                    <li>How do we protect your information</li>
                    <li>How do we store your information</li>
                    <li>How to update this policy</li>
                    <li>How do you contact us</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
